org.gephi.data.attributes.api
Interface AttributeValue

public interface AttributeValue

Cell that contains the value for a particular AttributeColumn and AttributeRow.

Cells are build from a AttributeValueFactory, that can be get from the AttributeModel.

Author:
Mathieu Bastian
